<head>Translation</head>
<p> Gaius Julius Nigerus, farewell.</p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>Lettering and formula alike suggest the early date. The dead man is likely to be connected with the Julian family - cf. C. Iulius Zoilos. (See name index s.v. <foreign lang="grc">Ζοῖλος</foreign>.)</p>
</div>
